        "review_body": "Lawrence Lovedale is a prestigious residential school located in Ooty, Tamil Nadu, India. The school is known for its excellent academic programs, state-of-the-art facilities, and experienced faculty members. The school offers education from kindergarten to grade 12 and follows the CBSE curriculum.\n\nThe school has a beautiful campus with lush green surroundings, which provides a serene and peaceful environment for learning. The classrooms are spacious and well-equipped with modern technology, making learning more interactive and engaging. The school also has a well-stocked library, science and computer labs, and a sports complex.\n\nThe faculty members at Lawrence Lovedale are highly qualified and experienced, providing students with the best possible education. The school also offers extracurricular activities such as sports, music, dance, and drama, which help students develop their skills and talents.\n\nThe school has a strong focus on discipline and character building, which helps students become responsible and well-rounded individuals. The school also has a strong alumni network, which provides students with opportunities for networking and career development.\n\nOverall, Lawrence Lovedale is an excellent school that provides students with a holistic education and prepares them for a successful future. The school's commitment to academic excellence, state-of-the-art facilities, and experienced faculty members make it a top choice for parents who want the best education for their children.\n\nAs a lawrencian this is my experience",
